OL,3,CCorrosion could be to blame for man
OL,4,Cfalling to his death from balcony -
OL,5,CExperts
OL,7,FA building expert has told ITV News
OL,8,FLondon that corrosion could be to
OL,9,Fblame for a man falling to his death
OL,10,Ffrom a balcony in central London.
OL,12,FJoshua Robbins, 23, went outside to
OL,13,Fcheck on a pizza delivery at his flat
OL,14,Fin Holborn when the railings gave way.
OL,16,FWe took a surveyor to Holland and
OL,17,FThurston Dwellings who said the
OL,18,Fbalconies needed regular safety checks.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
