FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1772193824
OL,3,CCorrosion could be to blame for man
OL,4,Cfalling to his death from balcony -
OL,5,CExperts
OL,7,FBuilding surveyor Mark Douglas said:
OL,8,F"We work with many housing
OL,9,Fassociations and boroughs all over
OL,10,FLondon and we've obviously said to
OL,11,Fthem they should carry an annual, if
OL,12,Fnot regular inspections of these sort
OL,13,Fof areas.
OL,15,F"Whether it's the facade, whether it's
OL,16,Fthe banished rods, whether it's the
OL,17,Frailings, they should be looked at and
OL,18,Fit should become some sort of
OL,19,Fcompliance should be adhered to."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1772193824
OL,3,CCorrosion could be to blame for man
OL,4,Cfalling to his death from balcony -
OL,5,CExperts
OL,7,FStructural engineer Tony O'Connor
OL,8,Fagreed: "The risk of death or the risk
OL,9,Fof accident from falling from failure
OL,10,Fof a balcony is much greater than an
OL,11,Finternal risk. So therefore, the
OL,12,Fbalcony should be inspected on a
OL,13,Fregular basis."
OL,15,FHe added: "The interesting thing here
OL,16,Fis that the balcony that are face
OL,17,Ffixed, I can't see any failure of the
OL,18,Fconcrete.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1772193824
OL,3,CCorrosion could be to blame for man
OL,4,Cfalling to his death from balcony -
OL,5,CExperts
OL,7,F"So it is suggesting maybe there was
OL,8,Ffailure in the balustrade, but I don't
OL,9,Fknow ... Possibly corrosion."
OL,11,FMr O'Connor also said flower pots that
OL,12,Fhung on the railings, which were
OL,13,Frecently removed, may have placed
OL,14,Fextra stress on the building.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1772193824
OL,3,CCorrosion could be to blame for man
OL,4,Cfalling to his death from balcony -
OL,5,CExperts
OL,7,F"Looking at the balconies and I mean,
OL,8,Fthey're small planters, they will have
OL,9,Fincreased the load on the balcony,
OL,10,Fpushing outwards, which is the way
OL,11,Fthat the failure occurred. But it
OL,12,Fshouldn't really have had that level
OL,13,Fof impact on a balcony."
OL,15,FThe housing association Islington and
OL,16,FShoreditch Housing Association (ISHA)
OL,17,Frecognised that Joshua's death has
OL,18,Fbeen "deeply distressing".
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
