CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1772193824
OL,3,CCorrosion could be to blame for man
OL,4,Cfalling to his death from balcony -
OL,5,CExperts
OL,7,FIts chief executive Pippa Fleetwood-
OL,8,FRead said: "We know his death has had
OL,9,Fa profound effect on his parents,
OL,10,Ffamily, friends and neighbours ` and
OL,11,Fwe offer our heartfelt and sincerest
OL,12,Fcondolences to them at this incredibly
OL,13,Fdifficult time.
OL,15,F"We are doing everything we can to
OL,16,Fsupport everyone living at Holland and
OL,17,FThurstan Dwellings, including offering
OL,18,Fcounselling support to everyone living
OL,19,Fthere and having a greater on-site
OL,20,Fpresence to listen directly to any
OL,21,Fconcerns residents may have."
OL,26,@wD@AOU
