OL,3,CCorrosion could be to blame for man
OL,4,Cfalling to his death from balcony -
OL,5,CExperts
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FJoshua's mum, Fiona Garrett, recently
OL,13,Ftold ITV News London she was worried
OL,14,Fit would take time to find out who was
OL,15,Fto blame.
OL,17,F"If my son, God forbid, had been
OL,18,Fmurdered, you would have someone to
OL,19,Factually say he's accountable, she's
OL,20,Faccountable, whereas this is a
OL,21,Ffaceless entity.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1772193824
OL,3,CCorrosion could be to blame for man
OL,4,Cfalling to his death from balcony -
OL,5,CExperts
OL,7,F"And even then I feel like it's going
OL,8,Fto end up like a Grenfell situation,
OL,9,Fwhere it's constantly passing the
OL,10,Fbuck."
OL,12,FMeanwhile the Metropolitan Police is
OL,13,Finvestigating.
OL,15,FThe force said: "Investigators are in
OL,16,Fthe process of liaising with expert
OL,17,Fwitnesses, including a forensic
OL,18,Fstructural engineer, as well as
OL,19,Fcarrying out interviews with witnesses
OL,20,Fand residents.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
