CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1772193824
OL,3,CCorrosion could be to blame for man
OL,4,Cfalling to his death from balcony -
OL,5,CExperts
OL,7,F"These enquiries can take some time
OL,8,Fgiven the nature of the investigation
OL,9,Fand complexities.
OL,11,F"The Coroner has been notified and a
OL,12,Ffull Coroner's report will be
OL,13,Fcompleted at the end of the police
OL,14,Finvestigation."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
