PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1772193824
OL,3,CCorrosion could be to blame for man
OL,4,Cfalling to his death from balcony -
OL,5,CExperts
OL,7,FISHA said it was co-operating with the
OL,8,Fpolice investigation, adding: "We hope
OL,9,Fpeople understand that whilst
OL,10,Finvestigations are ongoing it wouldn't
OL,11,Fbe right for us to comment further ...
OL,12,FWe hope that those investigations
OL,13,Fconclude swiftly so Joshua's family
OL,14,Fcan get the answers they seek."
